{"id":327317,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/327317","type":2,"name":"セブンナイツ レボリューション -英雄の継承者-","name_cn":"七骑士 革命 -英雄的继承者-","summary":"“為せ　汝の欲することを”\r\n\r\nかつて世界を救った英雄達がいた。\r\n数多の英雄達は〈破壊〉の力と戦い、\r\nこの世界を守ったのだ。\r\n\r\nそして、時は流れ――\r\n\r\n英雄たちは歴史の彼方へと去り、\r\n彼らの力を身に纏い戦う〈継承者〉と呼ばれる\r\n少年少女達に世界の運命は託されることとなった。\r\n\r\n〈継承者〉の頂点に立つ〈セブンナイツ〉の一人、\r\n少女ファリアは押し寄せる〈破壊〉の軍勢との戦いの中、\r\nネモと名乗る一人の少年を救う。\r\n\r\n激戦の中、\r\nネモは自らも知らぬままに〈英雄〉の力を喚起し、\r\n〈継承者〉としての力を振るう。\r\n\r\nだが、彼の〈英雄〉は\r\n誰も知らぬ、誰も語らぬ者だった。\r\n\r\nそしてこの時より始まるのだ。\r\n過去と現在の交錯する魂の旅路が――","air_date":"2021-04-04","air_weekday":7,"rating":{"total":37,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":5,"4":7,"5":10,"6":7,"7":4,"8":2,"9":0,"10":1},"score":5.1},"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/e8/eb/327317_uzufm.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e8/eb/327317_uzufm.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e8/eb/327317_uzufm.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/e8/eb/327317_uzufm.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e8/eb/327317_uzufm.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":30,"collect":3,"doing":86,"on_hold":10,"dropped":39},"crt":[{"id":91235,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/91235","name":"ネモ","name_cn":"","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/87/25/91235_crt_Cq52c.jpg?r=1613297784","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/87/25/91235_crt_Cq52c.jpg?r=1613297784","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/87/25/91235_crt_Cq52c.jpg?r=1613297784","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/87/25/91235_crt_Cq52c.jpg?r=1613297784"},"comment":0,"collects":1,"info":{"alias":{"romaji":"Nemo"},"gender":"男","source":"https://sevenknights-anime.jp/character/"},"actors":[{"id":10256,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/10256","name":"山下大輝","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b0/56/10256_prsn_p2A8G.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/b0/56/10256_prsn_p2A8G.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/b0/56/10256_prsn_p2A8G.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b0/56/10256_prsn_p2A8G.jpg"}}]},{"id":91236,"url":"http://bgm.tv